102
00:07:56.440 --> 00:07:58.859
Yeah? Well. the curious fish gets caught.

103
00:07:58.942 --> 00:08:01.445
We do not talk. think.
discuss. contemplate.

104
00:08:01.528 --> 00:08:04.114
