105
00:08:04.198 --> 00:08:05.365
Yes. Mom.

106
00:08:05.449 --> 00:08:07.576
Here. Now let's get back to work.

107
00:08:11.747 --> 00:08:13.165
Hey.

108
00:08:14.833 --> 00:08:16.335
