I just came for my stuff.

125
00:09:39.209 --> 00:09:40.210
Ooh.

126
00:09:41.211 --> 00:09:43.630
Uh. hey! Wait. that's mine!

127
00:09:48.677 --> 00:09:50.887
Sir? You forgot your harpoon and...

128
00:09:50.971 --> 00:09:52.347
