155
00:12:33.383 --> 00:12:34.551
Yeah. that's called phantom tail.

156
00:12:34.634 --> 00:12:35.635
You'll get used to it.

157
00:12:38.138 --> 00:12:39.931
Right. Walking.

158
00:12:40.098 --> 00:12:42.809
Don't worry. you're in luck.
I basically invented it.

159
00:12:42.976 --> 00:12:45.604
To start. stack everything
one on top of the other.

160
00:12:45.687 --> 00:12:47.272
Like a pile of rocks.

161
00:12:50.442 --> 00:12:52.277
Great! I mean. fine. whatever.

162
00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:54.488
Now. walking is just like swimming.

163
00:12:54.571 --> 00:12:56.448
But without fins. Or a tail.

164
00:12:56.531 --> 00:12:57.657
And also. there's no water.

165
00:12:57.741 --> 00:12:59.451
Otherwise. it's like the exact same thing.

166
00:12:59.534 --> 00:13:00.660
Give it a try.

167
00:13:02.704 --> 00:13:03.872
That's not it. Try it again.

168
00:13:05.290 --> 00:13:07.626
Oh. try to lead with your head.

169
00:13:07.709 --> 00:13:09.294
No. more belly.

170
00:13:11.296 --> 00:13:13.215
That's... That's lying on the ground.

171
00:13:13.298 --> 00:13:14.299
How about this?

172
00:13:14.382 --> 00:13:16.343
