not think about something.

175
00:13:20.180 --> 00:13:22.474
Okay. okay. Watch.

176
00:13:22.557 --> 00:13:24.518
Point your feet to where
you wanna go. Okay?

177
00:13:24.601 --> 00:13:26.728
And then you just catch yourself

178
00:13:26.811 --> 00:13:27.812
