179
00:13:30.899 --> 00:13:31.983
Yeah. that's right.

180
00:13:34.528 --> 00:13:35.529
Heh.

181
00:13:37.322 --> 00:13:39.074
Good. Good.

182
00:13:39.157 --> 00:13:41.618
