- I'm... I'm getting it!

183
00:13:42.452 --> 00:13:44.996
Not bad. kid. Alberto Scorfano.

184
00:13:45.080 --> 00:13:46.081
Luca Paguro.

185
00:13:49.042 --> 00:13:51.586
