189
00:13:59.636 --> 00:14:01.137
Mother-of-pearl!

190
00:14:01.763 --> 00:14:02.764
You live up here?

191
00:14:02.847 --> 00:14:04.140
Yeah. Me and my dad.

192
00:14:04.224 --> 00:14:05.308
He's not even here a whole lot.

193
00:14:05.392 --> 00:14:06.977
so I pretty much just do whatever I want.

194
00:14:07.060 --> 00:14:08.186
Isn't it dangerous?

195
00:14:08.270 --> 00:14:09.479
Yeah. it's the best!

196
00:14:09.563 --> 00:14:11.356
Everything good is above the surface.

197
00:14:11.773 --> 00:14:13.567
Like. what else?

198
00:14:14.025 --> 00:14:15.277
Air!

199
00:14:18.113 --> 00:14:20.448
Gravity! Also known as falling!

200
00:14:22.951 --> 00:14:25.745
The sky. Clouds. The sun.

201
00:14:26.037 --> 00:14:27.789
Whoa. Don't look at it.

202
00:14:27.872 --> 00:14:29.583
Just kidding. Definitely look at it.

203
00:14:31.167 --> 00:14:34.045
And then. there's human stuff.

204
00:14:37.382 --> 00:14:38.466
Whoa.

205
00:14:39.509 --> 00:14:40.510
As you can see.

206
00:14:40.594 --> 00:14:42.387
I've been collecting for a long time.

207
00:14:42.470 --> 00:14:43.471
so ask me anything.

208
00:14:46.057 --> 00:14:47.601
Whoa.

209
00:14:47.684 --> 00:14:50.103
Yes. That's the Magic
Singing Lady Machine.

210
00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:52.606
It's broken. unfortunately.

211
00:14:54.190 --> 00:14:56.568
Whoa! You unbroke it!

212
00:15:06.161 --> 00:15:07.162
What's that?

213
00:15:07.245 --> 00:15:10.248
Oh. it's just the greatest thing
that humans ever made.

214
00:15:10.332 --> 00:15:11.666
The Vespa.

215
00:15:11.750 --> 00:15:13.627
- Whoa.
- You just sit on it.

216
00:15:13.710 --> 00:15:15.587
and it takes you anywhere you wanna go.

217
00:15:15.670 --> 00:15:17.380
In the whole stinkin' world!

218
00:15:19.466 --> 00:15:21.509
"Vespa is freedom."

219
00:15:24.346 --> 00:15:25.347
Huh?

220
00:15:29.768 --> 00:15:30.769
Whoo-hoo-hoo.

221
00:15:30.852 --> 00:15:32.062
Yeah!

222
00:15:34.564 --> 00:15:35.565
Pretty cool. right?

223
00:15:35.649 --> 00:15:38.401
Uh... Yeah.

224
00:15:39.819 --> 00:15:41.988
Huh. Are you gonna make one?

225
00:15:42.072 --> 00:15:43.907
I think you have all the parts.

226
00:15:44.824 --> 00:15:46.409
I do have the parts.

227
00:15:46.493 --> 00:15:48.536
I am gonna make one! You wanna help?

228
00:15:48.620 --> 00:15:52.290
Me? Yeah! Wait! No. I can't.

229
00:15:52.374 --> 00:15:54.250
- I gotta go home.
- Right this second?

230
00:15:54.334 --> 00:15:56.628
Yeah. if my parents found out
I was up here...

231
00:15:56.711 --> 00:15:58.088
Oof.

232
00:15:58.171 --> 00:16:00.799
It would be bad. So. thank you. but...

233
00:16:03.134 --> 00:16:05.637
Goodbye. Forever.

234
00:16:08.648 --> 00:16:11.735
Okay. but now. I really do have to go.

235
00:16:11.818 --> 00:16:12.944
Okay. Bye.

236
00:16:14.738 --> 00:16:17.657
Seriously. I have to go.
like. now. Like. right now.

237
00:16:17.741 --> 00:16:18.992
Okay. See ya.

238
00:16:21.911 --> 00:16:23.538
It's even better than the picture.

239
00:16:23.622 --> 00:16:24.456
Yeah. it is.

240
00:16:25.248 --> 00:16:27.000
Gotta run.

241
00:16:27.542 --> 00:16:28.835
See ya tomorrow!

242
00:16:34.674 --> 00:16:36.301
Luca! Where have you been?

243
00:16:36.384 --> 00:16:37.385
Uh...

244
00:16:37.469 --> 00:16:39.179
<i>Don't say surface.
Don't say surface.</i>

245
00:16:39.262 --> 00:16:40.639
Surface.

246
00:16:40.722 --> 00:16:42.557
