- Gonna tell us where you were?

250
00:16:49.689 --> 00:16:51.566
- Uh...
- It's my fault.

251
00:16:51.650 --> 00:16:53.485
I sent him to look for sea cucumbers.

252
00:16:53.568 --> 00:16:56.488
Right! Sorry. Grandma.
I couldn't find them.

253
00:16:56.571 --> 00:16:57.781
Mom. his life is

254
00:16:57.864 --> 00:16:59.949
